    'services.module1.service2.title': 'Website Design & Development',
    'services.module1.service2.summary': 'Stunning, responsive websites that convert.',
    'services.module1.service2.phase1.title': 'Strategy & Research',
    'services.module1.service2.phase1.description': 'We analyze your market, audience, and goals to inform design and content. Our team reviews analytics, benchmarks competitors, and identifies opportunities for differentiation. We define user personas and map out key journeys. This research ensures your website is built for impact and engagement.',
    'services.module1.service2.phase2.title': 'Wireframing & UI/UX',
    'services.module1.service2.phase2.description': 'We create wireframes and design beautiful, user-friendly interfaces. Our process includes mood boards, style guides, and interactive prototypes. We focus on usability, accessibility, and brand consistency. You review and approve every step before development begins.',
    'services.module1.service2.phase3.title': 'Development',
    'services.module1.service2.phase3.description': 'We build your site with modern tech, ensuring speed, SEO, and accessibility. Our developers use responsive frameworks and optimize for all devices. We integrate CMS, analytics, and any required third-party tools. Rigorous testing ensures a flawless launch.',
    'services.module1.service2.phase4.title': 'Launch & Optimization',
    'services.module1.service2.phase4.description': 'We launch, monitor, and optimize your site for ongoing success. Our team tracks performance, user behavior, and conversion rates. We provide training, documentation, and ongoing support. Continuous improvements keep your site ahead of the competition.',
    'services.module1.service3.name': 'App',
    'services.module1.service3.title': 'Mobile App Development',
    'services.module1.service3.summary': 'iOS & Android apps for modern businesses.',
    'services.module1.service3.phase1.title': 'Ideation & Planning',
    'services.module1.service3.phase1.description': 'We define your app\'s purpose, features, and user flows through collaborative workshops. Our team researches user needs, market trends, and platform guidelines. We create detailed specifications and wireframes. This phase ensures your app is set up for success from the start.',
    'services.module1.service3.phase2.title': 'Design & Prototyping',
    'services.module1.service3.phase2.description': 'We design intuitive, engaging app interfaces and interactive prototypes. Our designers focus on usability, accessibility, and platform best practices. You review and test prototypes to ensure the app meets your vision and user expectations.',
    'services.module1.service3.phase3.title': 'Development',
    'services.module1.service3.phase3.description': 'We develop your app for iOS/Android with regular demos and feedback cycles. Our engineers use agile sprints, automated testing, and code reviews. We ensure performance, security, and scalability are built in from day one.',
    'services.module1.service3.phase4.title': 'Testing & Launch',
    'services.module1.service3.phase4.description': 'We test thoroughly and launch your app to the stores. Our QA team covers functional, device, and user acceptance testing. We handle app store submissions, compliance, and launch marketing. Your app goes live with confidence and support.',
    'services.module1.service3.phase5.title': 'Support & Updates',
    'services.module1.service3.phase5.description': 'We provide ongoing support, updates, and feature enhancements. Our team monitors analytics, user feedback, and platform changes. We proactively address issues and help your app evolve with your business.',
    'services.module1.service4.name': 'AI',
    'services.module1.service4.title': 'AI & Automation Solutions',
    'services.module1.service4.summary': 'Leverage AI to automate and innovate.',
    'services.module1.service4.phase1.title': 'Needs Assessment',
    'services.module1.service4.phase1.description': 'We evaluate your business for AI and automation opportunities. Our experts analyze workflows, data sources, and pain points. We identify high-impact areas for automation and innovation. This phase ensures AI is applied where it delivers real value.',
    'services.module1.service4.phase2.title': 'Solution Design',
    'services.module1.service4.phase2.description': 'We architect AI workflows and automation strategies tailored to your needs. Our team selects the right models, tools, and platforms. We design for scalability, security, and ethical use. You review and approve the solution before implementation.',
    'services.module1.service4.phase3.title': 'Implementation',
    'services.module1.service4.phase3.description': 'We build and integrate AI solutions into your business processes. Our engineers handle data integration, model training, and deployment. We ensure seamless adoption and minimal disruption to your operations.',
    'services.module1.service4.phase4.title': 'Monitoring & Optimization',
    'services.module1.service4.phase4.description': 'We monitor, optimize, and support your AI systems post-launch. Our team tracks performance, retrains models, and addresses issues proactively. Continuous improvement ensures your AI delivers ongoing value.',
